OL,3,CRoman skeleton found under extension
OL,4,Claid to rest
OL,6,FHuman remains dating back to Roman
OL,7,Ftimes that were unearthed during a
OL,8,Fproperty renovation have been laid to
OL,9,Frest during a ceremony in Lincolnshire.
OL,11,FThe bones were discovered by
OL,12,Fhomeowners on Brookside Close in
OL,13,FAncaster in March last year while
OL,14,Ffoundations were being dug for an
OL,15,Fextension.
OL,17,FTests by archaeological experts found
OL,18,Fthe remains to be Roman.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
