OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783689573
OL,3,CRoman skeleton found under extension
OL,4,Claid to rest
OL,6,FA Lincolnshire Police spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "As the remains could not be
OL,8,Freturned to their original resting
OL,9,Fplace, efforts were made to ensure
OL,10,Fthey could be reinterred with dignity."
OL,12,FA burial took place on 8 July during a
OL,13,Fshort ceremony at Wilsford Extension
OL,14,FGraveyard, attended by local residents.
OL,16,FOrganisers called the service a
OL,17,F"fitting and dignified conclusion to
OL,18,Fan unusual discovery" and thanked the
OL,19,Fcommunity for coming together to
OL,20,Fprovide a proper final resting place,
OL,21,Fand treating the remains with respect.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/2
